332
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:47,280
At Lover's Peak.

333
00:17:48,030 --> 00:17:48,590
What?

334
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,480
He died at Lover's Peak.

335
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:10,550
After being tortured by Ma Derong's men,

336
00:18:10,550 --> 00:18:12,680
