344
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,460
It was all to pay Li Dong's blackmail.

345
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:31,640
He was a college student.

346
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:33,270
Without using some extreme measures,

347
00:18:33,270 --> 00:18:35,160
