to pay back a debt.

349
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:38,480
He chose his own path.

350
00:18:39,220 --> 00:18:40,820
Let's not talk about Lu Ming.

351
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:42,030
But Li Dong

352
