378
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:21,240
[Computer Data Recovery]

379
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:22,100
Lin Hua, right?

380
00:20:25,350 --> 00:20:26,810
We're from
the Nanping Criminal Police Team.

381
00:20:26,810 --> 00:20:28,670
