giving birth to Shanshan.

399
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:00,810
Do you know

400
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:02,750
Li Dong?

401
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:08,350
Lu Ming once paid 200,000

402
00:22:08,510 --> 00:22:09,910
