438
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:21,310
This leg works fine.

439
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:22,110
It works fine.

440
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:23,310
Ouch!

441
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:25,640
Ouch!

442
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:27,150
Mr. Ma Jr.

443
00:25:27,510 --> 00:25:28,570
