444
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:29,920
Ouch!

445
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:31,070
Mr. Ma Jr.

446
00:25:32,430 --> 00:25:34,480
Ah.

447
00:25:44,590 --> 00:25:46,390
