463
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:36,830
Let's go down and check it out.

464
00:26:36,830 --> 00:26:37,510
Alright.

465
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:39,380
We split up to look for her.

466
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,730
By the time I found them,

467
00:26:43,480 --> 00:26:45,680
Lu Ming and Ma Ke were already fighting.

468
00:26:49,030 --> 00:26:50,570
After we knocked him out,

469
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,780
the shipyard suddenly exploded.

470
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:59,440
Our parents are all shipyard workers.

471
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:01,550
Our parents are all shipyard workers.

472
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:03,810
They were worried about their families,

473
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:07,000
