476
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:17,610
How did you kill him?

477
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:23,040
Not long after they left,

478
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:24,880
before they left.

479
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:28,130
I was staring at him.

480
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:34,840
The more I looked at him,
the angrier I became.

481
00:27:35,790 --> 00:27:36,850
So I picked up a rock

482
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:39,290
