501
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:03,480
Okay, I got it.

502
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:05,490
Thanks, everyone. Fall in!

503
00:30:08,480 --> 00:30:09,240
Wen.

504
00:30:09,750 --> 00:30:11,440
