523
00:30:42,590 --> 00:30:44,830
We have to speed up the investigation.

524
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:55,880
Rong.

525
00:30:57,150 --> 00:30:58,910
The police found Li Dong.

526
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,560
Lin Hua was also taken away.

527
00:31:07,790 --> 00:31:09,190
The police found Li Dong?

528
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,930
So, that guy's still alive?

529
00:31:11,950 --> 00:31:13,350
