537
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:36,160
Kang, do me a favor.

538
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:38,730
What are you going to do?

539
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,060
I'm going home.

540
00:31:49,130 --> 00:31:52,110
[Sancheng Financial Services]

541
