545
00:32:11,510 --> 00:32:13,370
Where exactly is the body hidden?

546
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,300
It's better if you two don't know.

547
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:21,590
I heard the shipyard
was laying people off.

548
00:32:21,590 --> 00:32:23,160
They didn't lay you off, did they?

549
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,480
No, I left on my own.

550
00:32:25,950 --> 00:32:26,830
Where'd you go?

551
00:32:27,310 --> 00:32:28,710
I'm a lighthouse keeper.

552
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,000
Living alone,

553
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:31,830
I don't have to
deal with the outside world.

554
00:32:31,830 --> 00:32:33,230
It's quiet and peaceful.

555
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:34,640
Lin Hua,

556
00:32:35,030 --> 00:32:37,490
you're not hiding anything from me,
are you?

557
00:32:43,730 --> 00:32:50,980
[Qin Wen]

558
00:33:02,240 --> 00:33:04,370
Did the police get anything out of you?

559
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:07,000
Where is Lin Hua?

560
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:13,300
Say something.

561
00:33:14,750 --> 00:33:15,680
Where is Lin Hua?

562
00:33:19,590 --> 00:33:20,440
He confessed.

563
00:33:23,550 --> 00:33:24,480
