567
00:33:33,510 --> 00:33:34,640
What about the body?

568
00:33:36,350 --> 00:33:37,720
Did he hand it over?

569
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:42,530
He won't hand over the body.

570
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:44,620
He can't even hand it over.

571
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:49,160
Where is the body?

572
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:52,440
Where is the body?

573
00:33:55,350 --> 00:33:56,240
Xia Xue.

574
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,380
I can't just

575
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:01,440
