577
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:06,370
We need to protect Shanshan, don't we?

578
00:34:06,750 --> 00:34:08,630
The shipyard explosion case
isn't that simple.

579
00:34:08,630 --> 00:34:11,150
As long as the shipyard explosion case
remains unsolved,

580
00:34:11,150 --> 00:34:13,010
Shanshan is in potential danger.

581
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:14,880
We can't waste the time

582
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:17,460
-the time Lin Hua bought for us.
-Lu Ming!

583
00:34:19,230 --> 00:34:21,510
I never wanted either of you

584
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:23,280
to shoulder everything.

585
00:34:24,110 --> 00:34:25,840
This all started because of me.

586
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:27,500
If it weren't for me back then,

587
00:34:27,710 --> 00:34:29,960
you two wouldn't be in this situation.

588
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:36,440
I can't let you
sacrifice yourselves for me anymore.

589
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:40,719
Tell me where the body is.

590
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:43,230
It's all over.

591
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:45,630
Xia Xue.

592
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:49,949
Xia Xue.

593
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:53,489
Let's make a promise, okay?

594
00:35:01,560 --> 00:35:02,420
Hello, Mr. Lin.

595
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:04,300
I'm your attorney.

596
00:35:05,070 --> 00:35:06,730
Mr. Lu asked me to tell you that

597
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:10,310
he won't leave the little frog
in the well forever.

598
00:35:10,710 --> 00:35:12,440
He will definitely get him out.

599
00:35:14,070 --> 00:35:16,070
The little fish in the pond are safe.

600
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:18,190
He won't let anyone hurt them.

601
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:19,600
Don't bother.

602
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:23,210
Tell Mr. Lu

603
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:26,320
it's all over.

604
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:29,610
Being friends with them

605
00:35:30,230 --> 00:35:32,030
is the happiest thing in my life.

606
00:35:37,230 --> 00:35:39,320
Please ask Mr. Lu for one last favor.

607
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,850
Take good care of my mom for me.

608
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:46,190
Okay.

609
00:35:46,510 --> 00:35:47,840
I'll be sure to tell him.

610
00:35:57,250 --> 00:35:58,250
[Name: Yao Zengxi]

611
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:00,500
Yao Zengxi?

612
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:01,630
Yes.

613
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:03,620
This photo doesn't look like you.

614
00:36:07,630 --> 00:36:08,030
Well...

615
00:36:08,030 --> 00:36:09,440
I used to be heavier.

616
00:36:11,800 --> 00:36:12,530
Fair enough.

617
00:36:12,910 --> 00:36:14,630
But you're a bit old.

618
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,280
I'm old, but I'm fit.

619
00:36:16,580 --> 00:36:18,780
Cleaning, stuff like that, no problem.

620
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:19,630
Okay.

621
00:36:20,110 --> 00:36:21,230
2,500 yuan per month,

622
00:36:21,230 --> 00:36:22,070
room and board included.

623
00:36:22,070 --> 00:36:22,670
You up for it?

624
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:23,670
No problem at all.

625
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:25,670
How about this...

626
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:27,040
2,000 yuan is enough.

627
00:36:27,230 --> 00:36:28,510
You keep the other 500

628
00:36:28,510 --> 00:36:30,040
for cigarettes and drinks.

629
00:36:30,800 --> 00:36:31,630
Very considerate.

630
00:36:31,630 --> 00:36:32,160
Alright.

631
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:33,540
Follow me to the dorms.

632
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:34,750
Thank you, thank you.

633
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:38,320
Lu Ming and Xia Xue's statements
are consistent.

634
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:41,000
Both said that Ma Ke raped Xia Xue.

635
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,590
After the three of them beat up Ma Ke,

636
00:36:42,590 --> 00:36:43,920
the shipyard suddenly exploded.

637
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:45,230
So they left the scene

638
00:36:45,230 --> 00:36:46,440
and rushed to the shipyard.

639
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:48,630
When they found out
Ma Ke was on the casualty list,

640
00:36:48,630 --> 00:36:50,610
they didn't look into it any further.

641
00:36:50,610 --> 00:36:52,800
Lin Hua's confession statement
says the same.

642
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:55,230
When Lu Ming and Xia Xue
heard about the shipyard explosion,

643
00:36:55,230 --> 00:36:57,110
they rushed there first,
and Lin Hua stayed behind.

644
00:36:57,110 --> 00:36:59,190
He killed Ma Ke in a fit of rage.

645
00:37:02,030 --> 00:37:03,000
Looking at it this way,

646
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:04,550
and based on the testimonies
of these three,

647
00:37:04,550 --> 00:37:06,080
it's absolutely flawless.

648
00:37:08,070 --> 00:37:10,730
If one person
can take the blame for everything,

649
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:13,030
why ruin three lives?

650
00:37:20,510 --> 00:37:21,360
You guys...

651
00:37:21,710 --> 00:37:22,880
Pick up the pace.

652
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:23,760
Okay.

653
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:25,320
We're moving too slowly.

654
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:28,500
This is a critical time for delivery.

655
00:37:28,510 --> 00:37:30,960
We must get this order done on time.

656
00:37:31,670 --> 00:37:32,800
We will. We promise!

657
00:37:44,780 --> 00:37:46,230
[Ma Ke]

658
00:37:46,260 --> 00:37:47,400
[Lu Ming, Xia Xue, Lin Hua]

659
00:37:47,430 --> 00:37:48,600
[Hou Shanshan, Hou Junjun, Ma Derong]

660
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:51,170
[Victims of the Shipyard Explosion]

661
00:37:54,820 --> 00:37:56,020
[Xia Gang, Xin Langyuan,
Sun Zhi, Wang Miaomiao]

662
00:37:56,030 --> 00:37:57,740
[The 13th Victim]

663
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:03,880
Boss,

664
00:38:06,750 --> 00:38:08,230
I've gone through

665
00:38:08,230 --> 00:38:09,710
every missing person report

666
00:38:09,710 --> 00:38:10,550
from the three months after the explosion.

667
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:11,960
They were either confirmed dead

668
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,230
or found alive later.

669
00:38:13,550 --> 00:38:15,280
No leads at all.

670
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:19,280
Hi, Chief Liu.

671
00:38:19,550 --> 00:38:21,280
How many nights have you been up?

672
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,540
Aren't you going home?

673
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:24,550
Go home and rest.

674
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:29,710
Why are you pulling my chair?

675
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:31,360
Pack up.

676
00:38:31,710 --> 00:38:33,030
Everyone, go home.

677
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:43,920
You can't work like this.

678
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:47,210
Come on, Mom Liu.

679
00:38:47,670 --> 00:38:48,630
Regarding the shipyard explosion case,

680
00:38:48,630 --> 00:38:50,670
a lot of new doubts
have come up in the case.

681
00:38:50,670 --> 00:38:52,150
We haven't figured them out yet.

682
00:38:52,150 --> 00:38:53,280
If you make me rest now,

683
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:54,480
how can I fall asleep?

684
00:38:54,630 --> 00:38:56,960
It's been years
since the shipyard explosion.

685
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,190
It's ancient history.

686
00:38:58,190 --> 00:38:59,760
You're still holding onto this case.

687
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:02,280
What's the point
of wearing yourself out like this?

688
00:39:02,280 --> 00:39:03,110
Stop talking.

689
00:39:03,510 --> 00:39:06,160
Hurry home, take a shower,
and get some sleep!

690
00:39:09,630 --> 00:39:10,280
Fine.

691
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:11,590
All right.

692
00:39:11,590 --> 00:39:13,880
You go back, wash up, and rest first.

693
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:15,630
I'll be there in a minute.

694
00:39:15,630 --> 00:39:16,280
Hurry up.

695
00:39:16,590 --> 00:39:16,920
Okay.

696
00:39:28,870 --> 00:39:33,400
[Qin Wen]

697
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:50,800
Hello.

698
00:39:51,090 --> 00:39:52,020
Who's speaking?

699
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:53,050
Captain Qin,

700
00:39:53,930 --> 00:39:54,390
it's me.

701
00:39:58,070 --> 00:39:58,800
Lu Ming?

702
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:02,330
Do you have time to meet?

703
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:06,440
Where?

704
00:40:06,790 --> 00:40:07,720
Tomorrow, 8 a.m.

705
00:40:08,590 --> 00:40:09,650
Nanping Cemetery.

706
00:40:27,120 --> 00:40:30,720
[The 13th Victim]
